OL,3,CPeter Mandelson: Can peerages be
OL,4,Crevoked?
OL,6,FMandelson, who served as US ambassador
OL,7,Ffor seven months, said he was
OL,8,Fresigning from the Labour Party on
OL,9,FSunday to avoid causing it "further
OL,10,Fembarrassment" after he was featured
OL,11,Fin the Epstein files.
OL,13,FThe documents suggest Epstein made
OL,14,F$75,000 (#55,000) in payments to
OL,15,FMandelson in three separate $25,000
OL,16,Ftransactions in 2003 and 2004.
OL,18,FMandelson said that he has no record
OL,19,For recollection of receiving the sums
OL,20,Fand did not know whether the documents
OL,21,Fwere authentic.
