OL,3,CPeter Mandelson: Can peerages be
OL,4,Crevoked?
OL,6,FThe 72-year-old was made a life peer
OL,7,Fin 2008 under Gordon Brown's
OL,8,Fgovernment, but has been on leave of
OL,9,Fabsence since last February.
OL,11,FSo could Mandelson's peerage be
OL,12,Frevoked, and what would that process
OL,13,Flook like? ITV News explains.
