OL,3,CPeter Mandelson: Can peerages be
OL,4,Crevoked?
OL,6,FMost members of the House of Lords are
OL,7,Flife peers. The opposition party can
OL,8,Falso appoint life peers.
OL,10,FCan a peerage be revoked?
OL,12,FA peerage can be removed, but it is a
OL,13,Fcomplex process because it can only be
OL,14,Fdone by an act of parliament, which
OL,15,Fwould involve introducing a new law.
OL,17,FIt currently cannot be removed in any
OL,18,Fother way - even the Crown, which
OL,19,Fappoints peerages, does not have the
OL,20,Fpower to cancel them.
