OL,3,CPeter Mandelson: Can peerages be
OL,4,Crevoked?
OL,6,FA law change to remove peerages last
OL,7,Fhappened more than 100 years ago, when
OL,8,Fthe Titles Deprivation Act 1917 (TDA)
OL,9,Fwas created after the First World War
OL,10,Fto remove peerages from "enemies" of
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,FFour members had their peerage removed
OL,14,Fin 1919 under the TDA. As this act
OL,15,Fspecifically relates to World War One,
OL,16,Fit's unlikely it could be used to
OL,17,Fremove peerages now.
OL,19,FCan a peer's membership be cancelled?
