OL,3,CPeter Mandelson: Can peerages be
OL,4,Crevoked?
OL,6,FIf the conviction is less than 12
OL,7,Fmonths, the case will be referred to
OL,8,Fthe House of Lords Conduct Committee
OL,9,Ffor it to recommend a sanction, the
OL,10,FHouse of Lords Library website says.
OL,12,FSeparately, the House of Lords Act
OL,13,F2015 also enables the expulsion or
OL,14,Fsuspension of members.
OL,16,FHowever, the conduct leading to
OL,17,Fexpulsion or suspension must have
OL,18,Fhappened before 2015, when the act
OL,19,Fcame into force. Or, the conduct must
OL,20,Fnot have been public knowledge before
OL,21,Fthe act was introduced.
