OL,3,CPeter Mandelson: Can peerages be
OL,4,Crevoked?
OL,6,FAs a life peer, Mandelson could resign
OL,7,Fvoluntarily from his membership in the
OL,8,FHouse of Lords. This would involve a
OL,9,Fwritten notice to the Clerk of the
OL,10,FParliament, and cannot be overturned.
OL,12,FAt the time of writing, it is unclear
OL,13,Fwhether Mandelson plans to resign from
OL,14,Fhis Lords membership.
